TY  - JOUR
TI  - Stock Market Prices and Volumes of Sales
AU  - Ying, Charles C.
AB  - [The relationships between stock prices and volumes of sales are examined with the view that they are joint products of a single market mechanism. The results found here tend to support the notion that any model of the stock market which separates prices from volumes or vice versa will inevitably yield incomplete if not erroneous results.]
