TY  - JOUR
TI  - Factor Market Distortions and the Shape of the Transformation Curve
AU  - Johnson, Harry G.
AB  - [It is shown geometrically and algebraically that a distortion in the factor market may make the transformation curve concave outward, either throughout or over a range, depending on the type of distortion. Also, computations are presented showing that it takes much factor market distortion to change the transformation curve appreciably.]
